{"tid":347757,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女學護上訴被拒　官：勿執迷不悟","createTime":"2017-08-05T05:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T06:31:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad38b9f8e801a3a23b60bc58f6f418770057d8f2","tid":347757,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170805/20112011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170805%2F20112011&d=vcaE0CmD7wU%2BBRZXB4nK2IS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=3140d03a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170805%2F20112011&h=e43008bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170805/20112011</a><br />\n<br />\n女學護上訴被拒　官：勿執迷不悟<br />\n<br />\n15,042<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170805/large/a1105a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170805%2Flarge%2Fa1105a.jpg&h=f67c7cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女學護簡媛茌用餐刀傷人，去年底被判入獄44個月。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【刀刺情夫案】<br />\n【本報訊】女學護戀上人夫3個月後被對方妻子揭發，分手後仍藕斷絲連，後來她乘對方到其家中短敍，突然用餐刀刺了對方7刀，並致電恐嚇對方母親。她於去年底因被裁定蓄意傷人及刑事恐嚇罪成立，被判囚44個月。她不服定罪，昨力數男事主供詞有多處漏洞欲提上訴，惟法官認為此非控罪關鍵，並指她的辯解不可信，勸她「唔好咁執迷不悟」，最終拒絕其上訴許可申請。<br />\n簡媛茌（29歲）上訴稱原審法官未有考慮男事主鄭柏堯（34歲）的供詞漏洞，包括案發當日鄭送院時清醒，卻未有向警察交代由上水至將軍澳的車程上發生何事，以及男事主聲稱被刺至滿身鮮血後爬行到停車場，但地上卻無血痕。<br />\n<br />\n指供詞完整與否非關鍵<br />\n惟法官彭偉昌強調現非重審，無論鄭作供時有無提及某點，均非控罪關鍵，最重要是要原審法官相信鄭的說法。彭官指鄭當時身受重傷，未能詳述案發細節屬合理，「人係有呢啲trauma（創傷），你做護士應該知」；又明言簡的自衞之說不可信，指簡當時僅手指、腳趾及膝蓋擦傷，惟鄭則被刺7刀且傷及腎臟，最終駁回簡的上訴許可申請。<br />\n案情指去年1月12日，簡在其上水寓所內先用不明液體潑向鄭，令其上衣有燒過的痕迹，再用餐刀刺他6刀。及後簡駕車送鄭回家，於車上再刺鄭一刀。簡於車上曾致電鄭母出言恐嚇「我唔擔保佢齊全返嚟」，鄭母遂報警。<br />\n案件編號：CACC384/16<br />\n■記者蘇曉欣  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n摸女途人臀　準新郎判社服"},{"pid":"d53c1be37f1851061d3f42dae5b0218e767e4b9b","tid":347757,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"這一次我執著面對　任性地沉醉<br />\n我並不在乎　這是錯還是對<br />\n就算是深陷　我不顧一切<br />\n就算是執迷　我也執迷不悔"},{"pid":"50038e369bfdb0150964849b9a4368e56d47c3c5","tid":347757,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"毫無悔意應該加刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314628cf53224c522bd300c6a4727c2d5a525999","tid":347757,"uid":121771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:06:03.000Z","msg":"把餐刀都咁勁， 佢又咁似大雄， 叮噹係唔係比咗佢 神奇餐刀"},{"pid":"a3832efaf8bb06bdc5ddf19a1a53d55b679e24d3","tid":347757,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:06:52.000Z","msg":"這次我重頭面對<br />\n過去和以後"},{"pid":"e96eab17797dc438a6774c6e02f736d7b6dec765","tid":347757,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170805/large/a1105a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170805%2Flarge%2Fa1105a.jpg&h=f67c7cb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9540daef9867914e3761e1c4a27da7a7b4f91678","tid":347757,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:10:52.000Z","msg":"陳淨心咁既樣"},{"pid":"42ae51906a8de8c2bf498d31f452d2a5388526dc","tid":347757,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:11:40.000Z","msg":"想養佢"},{"pid":"7d8ad30606eab5bb6c03c34c517d636c1d7229a1","tid":347757,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170805/large/a1105a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170805%2Flarge%2Fa1105a.jpg&h=f67c7cb2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>